Package se.arkalix.core.plugin.cp

Interface TrustedContractCounterOffer

  • All Superinterfaces:
    TrustedContractOffer
    public interface TrustedContractCounterOffer
extends TrustedContractOffer
    An offer countering a previously received such.

    Each counter-offer updates a so-called negotiation session, which contains all data currently associated with an on-going or previously closed negotiation.

    Instances of this type are trusted in the sense that they either (1) come from trusted sources or (2) will be sent to systems that trust their senders.
